import math

def calculate_gcd_probability(N):
    ans = 0
    x = math.floor(math.sqrt(N))
    i = 1
    while i <= x:
        ans += N // i
        i += 1
    ans /= 2
    ans -= x ** 2
    num = int(ans)
    den = N * N
    g = math.gcd(num, den)
    return (num // g, den // g)
